profile:
Welcome to Viktoria Professional Movers â€“ a company where customer care and satisfaction are our top priorities. 
 
There's no doubt about it, moving can be stressful!   Choosing responsible and experienced movers is one of the ways to alleviate that stress. When choosing a moving & storage company price is important, however the level of service your moving company provides you with is even more important, and often times cheap moving companies can end up costing you a fortune! Unfortunately, our industry abounds with companies whose aim to book as many jobs as they can by whatever means necessary. Many "lowball" estimates quickly balloon with unexpected charges while hurried workers provide disappointing service. For many of these companies protecting your property and ensuring your satisfaction is last on their list of priorities.
 
At Viktoria Professional Movers it's not about the number of moves, it's about the number of customers we leave happy & satisfied. Moving doesn't have to be complicated. Let us walk you through the process and get you on the way to a stress-free move to your new home. The key to a successful move is organization and we are the experts.
 
Whether you require moving, packing, or self-storage, you will never be just another client to us. Ever.
 
PIANO MOVING | PACKING MATERIALS | PACKING SERVICES, MOVING BIN RENTAL | STORAGE | SELF-STORAGE | LONG-DISTANCE MOVES | MOVING SUPPLIES

Real Estate Movers, with over 9 years of experience our crews will show you how we take pride in what we do every day. No move is to BIG or to SMALL, Real Estate Movers does it all! We offer competitively hourly rates in Calgary and flat rates on long distance moves across AB, BC, and SK. Customer satisfaction guaranteed! 

Locally operated in Alberta - Now offering Long Distance Moving Services across Canada.

profile:
A. Breton Relocations is a family owned and operated custom moving company servicing clients from British Columbia all the way to Ontario. Our offices are strategically located in Southern Ontario AND on Vancouver Island.
We can say with confidence your satisfaction, repeat business and referrals are our primary goal. We built our company and reputation with a simple yet important philosophy, Honesty ,Care and Respect for clients.
Not only am I the owner, I will also be at your residence in person with my exceptional hand picked crew to load up your belongings, drive them to your new destination and place every item into the exact location you desire. 
To assure quality I will be with you through the entire move. 

Our services include: Packing of Boxes, Dismantling of basic Furniture, Reassembling of Furniture, Moving of Household items Short/Long Distance, Special Handling for Art Work, Custom Transport for Motorcycles. 

All of our reviews on Homestars.com and The BetterBusinessBureau.com are from 100% real clients, we can also supply a reference list to validate our testimonials.  

What you will receive from Us:
Integrity, Honest and Accurate Quote, Highly Skilled and Friendly Crew, Fabulous New Equipment and above all a Stress Free Moving Experience.

Please call or email Dana Breton now for a free quote.

Sincerely
Adam Breton
Owner and Operator of A. Breton Relocations
